steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"736gs","text":"In each nucleofection, use 4 µg total of mRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"dth0s","text":"For prime editing PE2 strategy, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":18,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1h8bf","text":"    4 µg, IVT PE2 mRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e4llo","text":"    1.5 µl, 100 µM Synthetic pegRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"6jj1o","text":"For prime editing PE3 strategy, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":18,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"q3lg","text":"    4 µg, IVT PE2 mRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c6v7b","text":"    1 µl, 100 µM Synthetic pegRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"butsc","text":"    0.5 µl, 100 µM, Synthetic ngRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fpih4","text":"Pipet the proper amount of each component into a microcentrifuge tube.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
